WEBVTT

00:12:58.000 --> 00:13:00.296
it's just two sentences long --

00:13:00.320 --> 00:13:02.440
that captures how I feel now.

00:13:05.000 --> 00:13:08.096
"Your absence has gone through me

00:13:08.120 --> 00:13:10.640
like thread through a needle.

00:13:11.800 --> 00:13:15.280
Everything I do
is stitched with its color."

00:13:17.480 --> 00:13:20.760
For me that poem evokes my love for Paul,

00:13:21.520 --> 00:13:23.496
and a new fortitude

00:13:23.520 --> 00:13:26.560
that came from loving and losing him.

00:13:28.360 --> 00:13:30.760
When Paul said, "It's going to be OK,"